"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-03-05-marriage-can-wait-im-focused-one-final-push-olympic-glory-20405652\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The relationship between my brother Alistair and I is going to be so key now that we are inOlympic year and I can call on his experience as a double gold medallist.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 36, \"end\": 44, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The relationship\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 16}, {\"ngram\": \"my brother\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 35}, {\"ngram\": \"his experience\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"a double gold medallist\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alistair has retired from Olympic triathlon now but I am hoping to make the startline again inParismyself so a bit of advice here and there, now that we do not spend as much time together as we did, will be very useful.\", \"from\": 166, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 166, \"end\": 174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic triathlon\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"the startline\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 251}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 290}, {\"ngram\": \"as much time\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That said, while Alistair comes up with some nuggets, I do not always talk to him about emotional stuff.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some nuggets\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 439}, {\"ngram\": \"emotional stuff\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 490}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People also get motivation from such different places.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"motivation\", \"from\": 508, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"such different places\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Occasionally, if I am tired, I need and want a nice meal or a dog walk to look forward to, a holiday maybe.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nice meal\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"a dog walk\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"a holiday\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Alistair gets enough from his training - we are very different like that.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his training\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 698}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He does not need as much stuff outside of training to keep going.\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 799, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"as much stuff\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 764}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will talk to him about my preparation if, all being well, I go to the Games.\", \"from\": 801, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my preparation\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alistair has been so important for me when things have gone wrong.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 888, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Tokyo Olympics, he said to me ahead of the individual race: 'Believe in yourself.\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the individual race\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You are the best in this race, you are the only one who's been here and done this before and won medals.'\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has said similar things to me in the last year when things were not going as well for me.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"similar things\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1169}, {\"ngram\": \"the last year\", \"from\": 1179, \"to\": 1192}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He can be extremely blunt and I know if I have given him a really tough training session he will not say to me: 'You are fit, you are flying, that was a great session.'\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a really tough training session\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1324}, {\"ngram\": \"a great session\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I just know by how he is with me afterwards - if he is quiet, then I know I have hurt him in the session!\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the session\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are only certain things we do together now and he is away a lot, so it's not like we train together all the time.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only certain things\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know at some point we should look back and think about our careers but that's not something we have been able to do yet.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some point\", \"from\": 1652, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"our careers\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1735}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not great at looking at where we have come from to now.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know yet what lies after racing, I am not good at looking too far forward, but Alistair is giving talks and has a lot of things going on outside of his long-distance triathlon competitions.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1917, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"talks\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1955}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1965}, {\"ngram\": \"his long-distance triathlon competitions\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am getting married to Fiona on August 17 but before that there is the small matter of an Olympics I am trying to qualify for.\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\", \"score\": 0.9999999036419969, \"rank\": 9.629987064218916e-08, \"text\": \"Fiona\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2068}, {\"ngram\": \"the small matter\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We chose the date, six days after the Games finishes and two weeks after the triathlon, so that I could focus on Paris first.\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2271, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999933818344, \"rank\": 6.618097031795863e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the date\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2175}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2192, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"the triathlon\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The schedule then becomes very hard and so we thought that date would work best, so I can get married before the Super League season begins.\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_League\", \"score\": 0.9999818894205584, \"rank\": 1.688961540898179e-05, \"text\": \"Super League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Super_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The schedule\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have spent a decade making lots of my life decisions around triathlon.\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a decade\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2447}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"my life decisions\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2480}, {\"ngram\": \"triathlon\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it will be a very special day and I can not wait.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very special day\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no idea if I will have any time for a stag do!\", \"from\": 2554, \"to\": 2607, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will worry about that when I know my racing plans for the rest of the year.\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my racing plans\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"the year\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is plenty to come before I know if I will qualify.\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I am preparing as if I am going to France in the summer and all I can do is worry about myself.\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2783, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.8398070409290406, \"rank\": 0.1641880603258254, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the summer\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hate to fall into the trap of using sporting cliches but I am not getting carried away looking at other people's results.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trap\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting cliches\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"other people's results\", \"from\": 2945, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time - unlike previous Olympic years - I am not pre-selected.\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"previous Olympic years\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if my best is good enough to make the British team, it's good enough.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3078, \"end\": 3085, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8733804123840025, \"rank\": 0.09047712487948792, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it's not, it's not.\", \"from\": 3110, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I do not have many World Series races left in my career so Fiona will join me in Abu Dhabi after the race this weekend.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\", \"score\": 0.9999999036419969, \"rank\": 9.629987064218916e-08, \"text\": \"Fiona\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Princess_Fiona\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many World Series races\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3178}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"Abu Dhabi\", \"from\": 3222, \"to\": 3231}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unusually for me, we are staying on for a bit of a break so I can actually see the place rather than just land, compete and fly out again, as is more usual for most athletes.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 3311, \"to\": 3318}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3350}, {\"ngram\": \"just land\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3372}, {\"ngram\": \"most athletes\", \"from\": 3422, \"to\": 3435}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will definitely be strange for me so I am hoping to take it all in and use the short break for a rest after the race.\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3558, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the short break\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"a rest\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3549, \"to\": 3557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's time to make the most of every single moment of my career.\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3568}, {\"ngram\": \"every single moment\", \"from\": 3589, \"to\": 3608}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Have triathlon questions or simply need advice?\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3672, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"triathlon questions\", \"from\": 3629, \"to\": 3648}, {\"ngram\": \"advice\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just Ask AL!\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AL\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Introducing the world's first multi-sport AI, trained to offer expert advice ranging from beginners to elite athletes, directly from Alistair, Jonny and the team at Brownlee Fitness.\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3728, \"end\": 3730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9679559821225457, \"rank\": 0.033104829495245784, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.103366788349386e-20, \"text\": \"Alistair\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alistair_Brownlee\"}, {\"begin\": 3851, \"end\": 3859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"score\": 0.9976964412905938, \"rank\": 0.0021432315672641243, \"text\": \"Brownlee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Justin_Brownlee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"expert advice\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"beginners\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"elite athletes\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"Jonny\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3834}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Visitwww.brownleefitness.comfor info.\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Visitwww.brownleefitness.comfor info\", \"from\": 3869, \"to\": 3905}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:I am looking forward to retiring but not before beating the Chinese to Olympic gold in Paris ArrowMORE:The pressure for Paris gold is all internal as Olympic journey takes me full circle Get your favourite puzzles when they are ready to play on the website sent directly to you every day and track your daily streak!\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 4236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3978, \"end\": 3985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9865895368993747, \"rank\": 0.011424204998140555, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4005, \"end\": 4010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999933818344, \"rank\": 6.618097031795863e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4039, \"end\": 4044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999933818344, \"rank\": 6.618097031795863e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 3989, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"The pressure\", \"from\": 4021, \"to\": 4033}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic journey\", \"from\": 4068, \"to\": 4083}, {\"ngram\": \"full circle\", \"from\": 4093, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"your favourite puzzles\", \"from\": 4109, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4174}, {\"ngram\": \"your daily streak\", \"from\": 4216, \"to\": 4233}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This site\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4247}, {\"ngram\": \"reCAPTCHA\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4273}, {\